    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As the earth needs the clouds and the rain with the sunshine,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our souls need both sorrow and joy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So He places us oft in the fire of affliction"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The dross from the gold to destroy."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When He leads thru the valleys of trouble and sorrow,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His mercy and love there we trace;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the trials and sorrows He sends us in wisdom"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are part of His lessons in grace."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet how often we shrink from the purging and pruning,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Forgetting the Husbandman knows"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That the deeper and closer the cutting and paring,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The richer the cluster that grows."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O how well does He know that afflictions are needed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He has a wise purpose in view,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And within the dark valley He whispers to comfort,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Hereafter thou’lt know what I do.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we travel the pathway thru life’s shadowed valleys,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Fresh springs of His love ever rise;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we learn that our troubles, our sorrows and losses,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are blessings just sent in disguise."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So we’ll follow Him faithfully where’er He leadeth,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The pathway be dreary or bright;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For we’ve proved that our God is the “God of all comfort,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The God who gives songs in the night."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
